%% title: Submission and manual fallback sequence
%% purpose: Show normal submission gating and the bounded fallback path when support is unavailable or ambiguous.
sequenceDiagram
  participant Planner
  participant Reviewer
  participant Guard
  participant Submission
  participant AHJ
  participant Operator

  Planner->>Reviewer: Present sealed package + evidence
  Reviewer->>Guard: ReviewDecision(ACCEPT or dissent/block)
  Guard->>Submission: Allow submit only if preconditions pass
  Submission->>AHJ: Submit with idempotency key
  AHJ-->>Submission: Receipt or ambiguous/unsupported response
  alt receipt verified
    Submission->>Guard: submission_succeeded + receipt artifact
    Guard-->>Planner: case -> SUBMITTED
  else unsupported or ambiguous
    Submission->>Operator: ManualFallbackPackage required
    Operator->>Reviewer: proof bundle for validation
    Reviewer->>Guard: validated proof decision
    Guard-->>Planner: case -> SUBMITTED or remains blocked
  end
